init_text:
A woman has been dating guy after guy, but it never seems to work out. She’s unaware that she’s actually been dating the same guy over and over; a shapeshifter who’s fallen for her, and is certain he’s going to get it right this time.

One day,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The woman is so excited that she calls her best friend and tells her about the date.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The woman's friend is still not convinced.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The woman goes on a second date with the guy.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The woman is now certain that she's dating the same guy she's been dating all along.
